---
title: Cheesy Spinach Stuffed Chicken with Caprese Salad & Toasted Basil Ciabatta
description: Spinach always gives your plate needs a pop of color—but this leafy green has so much more to offer! That’s why our chefs finally gave spinach the starring role it deserves. Sautéed shallot and spinach are mixed with melty Italian cheese, then stuffed inside chicken that's topped with a golden panko crust. A garlicky sauce, caprese salad, and toasted ciabatta ties it all together. Show-stopping spinach? You saw it here first, folks!
